description: Selective AB test handling for funnels
globs: src/{middleware.ts,funnels/**,app/__funnels/**}
alwaysApply: false
---

# Selective AB Testing

- A/B logic is enabled only when `abTest.enabled` is true in funnel registry.
- Funnel without A/B uses a single config and must skip variant assignment.
- Persist selected variant with per-funnel cookie key.
- Variant values must be constrained to declared variants.
- Do not apply global randomization to all funnels.
